{"tid":1389030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工心理學","createTime":"2019-07-30T20:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:00:47.000Z","uid":59815,"like":257,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"25c37b1b0e68cd10d85c7926d055136092ffdce1","tid":1389030,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:40:23.000Z","msg":"要參加罷工，打工仔最擔心兩樣野：<br />\n一、失去工作<br />\n二、得自己罷出去柒，原來最後無人一齊<br />\n第一點，唔使解釋。點解決？要靠人多，唔單止係出到黎大集會人多，重要係自己公司入面夠人多。雖然今次罷工係勞資合作（商界暗中都反送中，都唔想警黑治港，但佢地無政治意志）但腦細都有可能秋後算賬。不過如果公司有70％人都參罷工，佢要針對邊個？佢可以炒70％人請返曬藍屍咩？無可能。<br />\n<br />\n第二點其實同第一點相關，罷工唔可以好似之前咁宣傳，就算200萬和理非遊行，佢地返到office，唔一定係多數。所以罷工宣傳一定要入到職場office，要俾人感受到自己係office之中既多數，佢地先至會行出黎。如果返到office自己係少數，被排斥，最後被炒，自然唔會行出黎啦。所以，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">響罷工之前，一個顯眼、能夠清晰地表態既象徵，係非常之咁重要，直接影響正式罷工日的成果。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《Secrets of a Successful Organizer》裏面，有一個例子，講芝加哥教師工會Chicago Teachers Union 點樣響一個工業行動入面相認，知道其他人係同路人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://labornotes.org/sites/default/files/styles/833x403/public/main/articles/chi-strike.jpg?itok=KDBC4tG3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flabornotes.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F833x403%2Fpublic%2Fmain%2Farticles%2Fchi-strike.jpg%3Fitok%3DKDBC4tG3&h=1e66e996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2012年，當芝加哥的教師們逐步開展罷工時，他們運用了一種熱身策略，叫每個工會會員在每週五穿紅衣。這是為了讓大家為更大的行動做好準備，同時評估工會支持度的增長進度。</span></strong></em><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>周五紅衣日既好處係，參加既門檻好低，唔影響工作，表面上亦都好溫和。而更加重要既係，令到想參加8.5罷工既人，心中有底，建立信心。</strong></span><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">剛開始，許多會員在星期五那天只是披了條紅圍巾或是穿上紅色圖案的襯衫。但舉目所見大家打消了顧慮。<span style=\"color: red;\">當校園處處一片紅，猶豫不決的同事就會明白，工會獲得了越來越多的支持。</span>工會代表也可以借助每周一次的活動，定期跟同事們交談，交談則是進一步組織的機會。</span></strong></em><br />\n最後，90％教師及98％投票會員授權工會發動罷工，成就左2012芝加哥教師罷工<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2012/09/19/us/illinois-chicago-teachers-strike/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2012%2F09%2F19%2Fus%2Fillinois-chicago-teachers-strike%2Findex.html&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=018dfa11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2012%2F09%2F19%2Fus%2Fillinois-chicago-teachers-strike%2Findex.html&h=5546cd6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2012/09/19/us/illinois-chicago-teachers-strike/index.html</a>。罷工歷時5日，26000教師響應，最後爭取到改善合約。成果不講太多，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最重要既係，一場26000人參加既罷工，一開始係由「紅衫行動」咁和理非既行動開始，令到教師建立到信心。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n職工盟都呼籲人8.5大罷工，重叫人8.2果日戴上白手帶，都係同一個道理。白手帶門檻係咪高過黑衫少少？係，但既然係要罷工，咁都係要高門檻少少。下面係職工盟個call，大家努力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67813927_3077323242307928_1468156474747256832_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_eui2=AeFsLSVcht5wdmQwPBvg_aEFzLtZYjwGMOaomsp7rr26i2h75OmLnXKuFnDNS1sfPTSEXuKIvmzzREnuG4AOCWWnqtiTWqq68vT3EFpQb8vbyg&amp;_nc_oc=AQn3zlPgUOZeRJpGFKY9LhTRibnPXRB4o2FFapD_hDtKxxwQWPA8FDeYVpXfDLfLUoY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=9e629a43cc9ad41ed6944cb63c675049&amp;oe=5DE9A32F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67813927_3077323242307928_1468156474747256832_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_eui2%3DAeFsLSVcht5wdmQwPBvg_aEFzLtZYjwGMOaomsp7rr26i2h75OmLnXKuFnDNS1sfPTSEXuKIvmzzREnuG4AOCWWnqtiTWqq68vT3EFpQb8vbyg%26_nc_oc%3DAQn3zlPgUOZeRJpGFKY9LhTRibnPXRB4o2FFapD_hDtKxxwQWPA8FDeYVpXfDLfLUoY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D9e629a43cc9ad41ed6944cb63c675049%26oe%3D5DE9A32F&h=a0c182d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><br />\n【表態，是作為港人的基本道義】2/8白手帶行動<br />\n我等知道社會各界有意於8月5日當日發起全港三罷，我們明白面對罷工，每人都會有自己的考慮，在大是大非之際，表態，是作為港人的基本道義。我們首先呼籲各業界在8月2日當日，不但出席公務員的集會，更加在當日自製一條白手帶，扣在手上，以示對8月5日罷工的支持。</em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5050fbed1bee87d1e7ad15b979e7ef6935308e3c","tid":1389030,"uid":5422,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:43:23.000Z","msg":"我8月5號一定罷"},{"pid":"3a41986d2e711d662c49e5b6f31f102345558f2f","tid":1389030,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:38:56.000Z","msg":"晨早一pish"},{"pid":"8bc2d2adaa2128d7d80747e803e45902e0c2aa69","tid":1389030,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2946a5dcfc91ae89d48da7318b4ab81f72fd6b0f","tid":1389030,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1a830ba2e488145b1db758c4eb7d9f8645d2309","tid":1389030,"uid":264434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee113501be47c7281b77f8471025d60ff50f552b","tid":1389030,"uid":255940,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n分析完全正確<br />\n人就係咁 大家一齊先敢行<br />\n香港人唔興表態 變左好多時以為人地同自己唔同諗法<br />\n示威係咁 衝擊係咁 罷工一樣係咁<br />\n<br />\n我地要夾好一個示意表態方法<br />\n大家暗地裡表態 而又唔會有任何風險<br />\n到大家見到支持者佔大多數 再發動罷工<br />\n成件事就好順理成章 循序漸進"},{"pid":"d3192d5573a0593c714530d47fcfd70b5dc1c4bb","tid":1389030,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5471254f9fe31566ec5abef4799f5e4168eb5941","tid":1389030,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22f6d838ef68e20bc90def5edacef94b848d591c","tid":1389030,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1408b9308485659afa5d98ec9a81efc35e40e51d","tid":1389030,"uid":69334,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"有啲人連少一日人工都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 已請no pay"},{"pid":"f734301d15150ac6bcc8fc7cd510bc6f000cc2a0","tid":1389030,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係香港人 我哋會加工"},{"pid":"5532143494737b4eaf71d059b662576cdf6d132f","tid":1389030,"uid":45100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"612果日成間公司幾十人得我一個沒番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6722a4385e41bac13c98e491759c6fce59e3bb","tid":1389030,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私咁，過埋2047都死左啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"bedb776f350fd439a3ea788a45e2b252193d1170","tid":1389030,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"支持，我冇野講"},{"pid":"44b2205bce241951d25294c676a56005bb712e49","tid":1389030,"uid":203535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/fac