eplyTime":"2019-07-31T03:31:57.000Z","msg":"好型啊！支持"},{"pid":"39121b3b55ce0cbb8bd6692ca9fd73da8780054a","tid":1389030,"uid":220977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n白絲帶唔知邊到搵<br />\n係咪應該星期五黑衫日會好d"},{"pid":"d007abbd247f7868cbd06c05c9a6e5cc25c98f11","tid":1389030,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[ 罷工文宣！Fb IG 瘋狂加hashtag ! ] <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷工要多人參與，<br />\n<br />\n除左罷工前集會集氣、各類街站連儂牆文宣<br />\n<br />\n亦都快d瘋狂去fb / ig 加 以下hashtag增加市民參與度！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hf7ppz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hf7ppz.png&h=37691996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkS5Vwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkS5Vwe.png&h=b234ed26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/hWh5Sax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWh5Sax.jpg&h=f682f165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/TZSULu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZSULu5.jpg&h=90f35e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之要用盡所有方法，<br />\n最簡單直接地，<br />\n令全部人都知道8月5日係罷工日！！！！<br />\n</span><br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas