d":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:26:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b3eedf53d43f0573fb43717953efbec3cd9e0cc","tid":1389030,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458a1509054574ab4b3a11bc1fc6b55a1bff15e2","tid":1389030,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5440933ccb140d74043a3c96fa570ed5160ee634","tid":1389030,"uid":138410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa60c070dca0644512e0b8023af21c0695673e","tid":1389030,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:48:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05fd6a1aa0869641911150105092031823dc6ce7","tid":1389030,"uid":272060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:57:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f5fbb82d377bb18a6e001a4ba12b904caaffd6","tid":1389030,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83cae7833dee886648c7893573910d192d7bad01","tid":1389030,"uid":272592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c37b1b0e68cd10d85c7926d055136092ffdce1","tid":1389030,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:40:23.000Z","msg":"要參加罷工，打工仔最擔心兩樣野：<br />\n一、失去工作<br />\n二、得自己罷出去柒，原來最後無人一齊<br />\n第一點，唔使解釋。點解決？要靠人多，唔單止係出到黎大集會人多，重要係自己公司入面夠人多。雖然今次罷工係勞資合作（商界暗中都反送中，都唔想警黑治港，但佢地無政治意志）但腦細都有可能秋後算賬。不過如果公司有70％人都參罷工，佢要針對邊個？佢可以炒70％人請返曬藍屍咩？無可能。<br />\n<br />\n第二點其實同第一點相關，罷工唔可以好似之前咁宣傳，就算200萬和理非遊行，佢地返到office，唔一定係多數。所以罷工宣傳一定要入到職場office，要俾人感受到自己係office之中既多數，佢地先至會行出黎。如果返到office自己係少數，被排斥，最後被炒，自然唔會行出黎啦。所以，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">響罷工之前，一個顯眼、能夠清晰地表態既象徵，係非常之咁重要，直接影響正式罷工日的成果。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《Secrets of a Successful Organizer》裏面，有一個例子，講芝加哥教師工會Chicago Teachers Union 點樣響一個工業行動入面相認，知道其他人係同路人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://labornotes.org/sites/default/files/styles/833x403/public/main/articles/chi-strike.jpg?itok=KDBC4tG3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flabornotes.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F833x403%2Fpublic%2Fmain%2Farticles%2Fchi-strike.jpg%3Fitok%3DKDBC4tG3&h=1e66e996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2012年，當芝加哥的教師們逐步開展罷工時，他們運用了一種熱身策略，叫每個工會會員在每週五穿紅衣。這是為了讓大家為更大的行動做好準備，同時評估工會支持度的增長進度。</span></strong></em><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>周五紅衣日既好處係，參加既門檻好低，唔影響工作，表面上亦都好溫和。而更加重要既係，令到想參加8.5罷工既人，心中有底，建立信心。</strong></span><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">剛開始，許多會員在星期五那天只是披了條紅圍巾或是穿上紅色圖案的襯衫。但舉目所見大家打消了顧慮。<span style=\"color: red;\">當校園處處一片紅，猶豫不決的同事就會明白，工會獲得了越來越多的支持。</span>工會代表也可以借助每周一次的活動，定期跟同事們交談，交談則是進一步組織的機會。</span></strong></em><br />\n最後，90％教師及98％投票會員授權工會發動罷工，成就左2012芝加哥教師罷工<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2012/09/19/us/illinois-chicago-teachers-strike/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2012%2F09%2F19%2Fus%2Fillinois-chicago-teachers-strike%2Findex.html&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=018dfa11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2012%2F09%2F19%2Fus%2Fillinois-chicago-teachers-strike%2Findex.html&h=5546cd6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2012/09/19/us/illinois-chicago-teachers-strike/index.html</a>。罷工歷時5日，26000教師響應，最後爭取到改善合約。成果不講太多，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最重要既係，一場26000人參加既罷工，一開始係由「紅衫行動」咁和理非既行動開始，令到教師建立到信心。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n職工盟都呼籲人8.5大罷工，重叫人8.2果日戴上白手帶，都係同一個道理。白手帶門檻係咪高過黑衫少少？係，但既然係要罷工，咁都係要高門檻少少。下面係職工盟個call，大家努力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67813927_3077323242307928_1468156474747256832_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_eui2=AeFsLSVcht5wdmQwPBvg_aEFzLtZYjwGMOaomsp7rr26i2h75OmLnXKuFnDNS1sfPTSEXuKIvmzzREnuG4AOCWWnqtiTWqq68vT3EFpQb8vbyg&amp;_nc_oc=AQn3zlPgUOZeRJpGFKY9LhTRibnPXRB4o2FFapD_hDtKxxwQWPA8FDeYVpXfDLfLUoY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=9e629a43cc9ad41ed6944cb63c675049&amp;oe=5DE9A32F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67813927_3077323242307928_1468156474747256832_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_eui2%3DAeFsLSVcht5wdmQwPBvg_aEFzLtZYjwGMOaomsp7rr26i2h75OmLnXKuFnDNS1sfPTSEXuKIvmzzREnuG4AOCWWnqtiTWqq68vT3EFpQb8vbyg%26_nc_oc%3DAQn3zlPgUOZeRJpGFKY9LhTRibnPXRB4o2FFapD_hDtKxxwQWPA8FDeYVpXfDLfLUoY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D9e629a43cc9ad41ed6944cb63c675049%26oe%3D5DE9A32F&h=a0c182d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><br />\n【表態，是作為港人的基本道義】2/8白手帶行動<br />\n我等知道社會各界有意於8月5日當日發起全港三罷，我們明白面對罷工，每人都會有自己的考慮，在大是大非之際，表態，是作為港人的基本道義。我們首先呼籲各業界在8月2日當日，不但出席公務員的集會，更加在當日自製一條白手帶，扣在手上，以示對8月5日罷工的支持。</em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0bae565eafaca152bd285a73f90334f080530234","tid":1389030,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"我聽日會帶白手帶返工，你呢？"},{"pid":"de901d0946363b4e0c1d5938b4c496678d4191b9","tid":1389030,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"49e516719a03c6991e46fe1d336742da7cf93a01","tid":1389030,"uid":131271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/